{"tid":2464242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾志偉睇「惡搞姜濤」拍手掌叫好","createTime":"2021-03-27T10:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T10:24:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":24,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a6e67e0573c7b44483490d815a0c2bb22c8934","tid":2464242,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQwXRfBhC2tnX4fYjAmoddzyPNJdbuD6WmM5AC6keou8W?filename=8fmp9bq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8fmp9bq.png&h=d0ec4d0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無綫日前舉行綜藝節目記者會，為搞氣氛，竟然惡搞對台的人氣王姜濤，結果引爆連串「關公災難」。當日台上的鄧智堅扮「薑蓉」，即被司儀之一的麥美恩撲出來追打，大嗌：「收聲啦！」馮盈盈則尖叫說：「你夠膽嚟踩場？打到你變薑蓉！」Bob亦附和大叫：「𡁻佢！打佢！」現場一片歡呼聲<strong>，連剛上任的無綫副主席曾志偉在台下睇到拍爛手掌</strong>，明顯好滿意一班藝人的表現，但就遭網民指他們以低劣手法打擊對手，行為小學雞之餘，亦有失大台身份。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210327/OGRY5RIULJGGXHMSVWKS6KMW5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210327%2FOGRY5RIULJGGXHMSVWKS6KMW5Y%2F&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr3wUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=42ae779e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210327%2FOGRY5RIULJGGXHMSVWKS6KMW5Y%2F&h=dc96113b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210327/OGRY5RIULJGGXHMSVWKS6KMW5Y/</a>"},{"pid":"bf3fa03d8f95e9dc8c8a43e699d7b1555d978384","tid":2464242,"uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"而家cctvb高層既質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd71e66d3bc0d2441af550d558f8a891861235f2","tid":2464242,"uid":62226,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:08:46.000Z","msg":"TVB 記招 有藝人扮姜濤 被指要打到佢變姜蓉  網民：低質、老土又肉酸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2463944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2463944</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢度已經討論緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/